PUT http://localhost:5001/write-around/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Product Name",
  "price": 150.00
}

### Example Usage
# To update an existing product by ID, use this payload
PUT http://localhost:5001/write-around/products/44
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "price": 89.99
}